{"tid":571461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九巴車長罷駛】九巴高層邀葉蔚琳周一會面　月薪車長大聯盟：創造歷史一刻 (00:03)","createTime":"2018-02-24T16:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T16:41:06.000Z","uid":117837,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee7d7ee9430dbb6e0e6b3345edcdf19361842bc","tid":571461,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:28:07.000Z","msg":"【九巴車長罷駛】九巴高層邀葉蔚琳周一會面　月薪車長大聯盟：創造歷史一刻 (00:03)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180225/s00001/d57d69c8fec09185c10acbadfe2eaae1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180225%2Fs00001%2Fd57d69c8fec09185c10acbadfe2eaae1.jpg&h=417737c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - 葉蔚琳舉手致意。（樊銳昌攝）<br />\n<br />\n九巴「月薪車長大聯盟」發動車長星期六（24日）晚8時起罷駛，抗議資方薪酬調整安排，只獲極少數車長響應。惟發起人葉蔚琳其後表示，會到九巴車廠會合其他參與行動的車長，之後到禮賓府外靜坐。九巴僱員工會亦指，若公司因停駛行動解僱任何員工，或會考慮以工會名義發起大罷工。<br />\n近午夜時分，傳出九巴車廠總經理彭樹雄到場，並透過公關人員跟參與今次工業行動的車長傳話。工業行動其後暫時停止，停駛巴士開始駛走。最後，有九巴高層擬邀約葉蔚琳星期一（26日）會面，工會暫未定是否參與，惟月薪車長大聯盟稱，已創造歷史一刻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180225/s00001/1519488008254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180225%2Fs00001%2F1519488008254&d=HfNrgXPymsOIlUf6%2B%2FTneL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4927a35a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180225%2Fs00001%2F1519488008254&h=f292f0da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180225/s00001/1519488008254</a>"},{"pid":"1515dfdb26b850a1c564266dec17512612eb7af0","tid":571461,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"九巴阿姐成功俾九巴高層撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2974eb9304018e1e2b9080dd2bd165c7b0e1f2a","tid":571461,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"未傾都階段性勝利<br />\n拍手慶祝下先啦"},{"pid":"8e02af22c29be5caae35cc49a7a24aea23fbaa40","tid":571461,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"到咗星期一，高層：你已經唔係我員工喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae5f6f71954c4b63a2c64a2f75b1a604a41cf49","tid":571461,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46d003d652a074eff5a46398d33886b57f8dbd78","tid":571461,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fae5f6f71954c4b63a2c64a2f75b1a604a41cf49","tid":571461,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:33:17.000Z","msg":"星期一<br />\n你係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公司炒咗你喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cb81398d8d0ea6f2ce6a861a02997fa4fea09e","tid":571461,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"把獎金廢除<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">將獎金條數撥入底薪</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無左原本筆獎金, 咁都有人覺得加左人工<br />\n<br />\n咪玩啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣撚左Roadshow 條數又唔見撥返入營運利潤<br />\n日日要人睇巴士站個報車mon, 有3份2 係廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7d474dfe56966fb8832b77c29b69b7f9e26513","tid":571461,"uid":37723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"高層: 比我中出完再幫我含撚咪加 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178d9623db12c4f46557cbe4